{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He presses the object - a cattle prod - under the SIGNALER's arm near his heart.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The SIGNALER instantly goes into convulsions, falling to the floor gasping and groaning.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Several SECURITY GUARDS grab the SIGNALER as he falls.
