{DIALOGUE}: Can you do it with your left hand?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SIGNALER
{DIALOGUE}: Well, I..
{DIALOGUE}: I never tried.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ACE
{DIALOGUE}: So, you're a righty?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SIGNALER
{DIALOGUE}: Ye-yeah.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ACE nods to one of the GUARDS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Instantly a large rubber mallet smashes onto the man's right hand four times to the sound of screams.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ACE watches.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ACE
