{CHARACTER_NAME}: GREEN
{DIALOGUE}: Sam has established himself as an indispensable member of the gaming community.
{DIALOGUE}: As the head of the Tangiers Gaming Corporation, it's my pleasure to welcome Sam Rothstein to the Vegas Valley Country Club.
