{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It reads: 'This Certificate of Appreciation.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sam Rothstein.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Charitable Foundations of Greater Las Vegas'.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They shake hands for the photographers.
