{META_DATA}: (Into the microphone)
{DIALOGUE}: It's with great pleasure that I accept this certificate of appreciation from the...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CAMERA TILTS UP TO A MOUNTED PLAQUE ON THE WALL, READING: 'CHARITABLE FOUNDATIONS OF GREATER LAS VEGAS'.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. VEGAS VALLEY COUNTRY-CLUB BANQUET ROOM - NIGHT
