{DIALOGUE}: Forget it.
{DIALOGUE}: You can't even set foot in the parking lot.
{DIALOGUE}: That's how serious it is.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: NICKY
{DIALOGUE}: In other words, I'm fucked.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ACE
{DIALOGUE}: In so many words, yes.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ACE (V.O.)
{DIALOGUE}: It just didn't sink into his head about the Black Book and what it meant.
