{DIALOGUE}: I mean, you're listed in there with Al Capone.
{DIALOGUE}: But Nicky didn't care.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: NICKY
{DIALOGUE}: I gotta do somethin'.
{DIALOGUE}: I gotta do somethin'.
{DIALOGUE}: They ain't gettin' rid of me.
{DIALOGUE}: They're not gettin' rid of me.
{DIALOGUE}: I'm staying here.
{DIALOGUE}: Fuck 'em.
{DIALOGUE}: Fuck 'em.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. GOLD RUSH JEWELER'S - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: WE MOVE PAST THE SKULL OF A STEER MOUNTED ON AN EXTERIOR WALL AND A WOODEN CIGAR STORE INDIAN STATUE, TO REVEAL DOMINICK SANTORO (WHO LOOKS A LITTLE LIKE HIS BROTHER NICKY) AND MARINO WHO ARE WAITING INSIDE THE GOLD RUSH.
