{CHARACTER_NAME}: CHARLIE CLARK
{DIALOGUE}: Yeah, that works out.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: NICKY (V.O.)
{DIALOGUE}: But how much cash could I bury in my closet, right?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: CHARLIE CLARK
{DIALOGUE}: You need to understand, and I - I'm sure you do... that in a venture of this kind, you have to be prepared to take some kind of loss.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: NICKY
{DIALOGUE}: Oh, listen, I understand that there's always a risk... you know, I might have to take a loss somewhere.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: NICKY (V.O.)
{DIALOGUE}: So I put some of the money into legitimate deals with Charlie Clark.
{DIALOGUE}: He was Ace's banker.
