{DIALOGUE}: Is that the last one?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: COOK
{DIALOGUE}: Yeah.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He hands the sandwich to DOMINICK who spits in it.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: NICKY (V.O.)
{DIALOGUE}: I had my kid brother, Dominick, run it for me.
