{META_DATA}: (Spits)
{DIALOGUE}: Fuckers!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: DOMINICK wraps it in plastic and puts it into a brown paper bag.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. LEANING TOWER RESTAURANT - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: DOMINICK sets the bag with the wrapped sandwich in it on top of pizza boxes being held by two uniformed Vegas COPS.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: DOMINICK
