{DIALOGUE}: It's not like I'm sleeping with the guy!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ACE
{DIALOGUE}: Yeah, how do I know?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: GINGER
{META_DATA}: (Sobbing)
{DIALOGUE}: You can't make me stop caring...
