{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. ACE'S HOUSE - NIGHT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ACE is watching the television news which features his photo and a police photo of NICKY.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: NEWSCASTER
{META_DATA}: (On television)
{DIALOGUE}: A Gaming Control Board investigation of Tangiers executive Sam Rothstein's application for a (photo of ACE) gaming license is underway.
