{CHARACTER_NAME}: STONE
{DIALOGUE}: I don't know
{META_DATA}: (Sighs.)
{CHARACTER_NAME}: GAGGI
{DIALOGUE}: What's he doin'?
{DIALOGUE}: He knows all those guys he yelled at are friends of ours.
{DIALOGUE}: What's the matter with him, making all this mess?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: STONE
{DIALOGUE}: Maybe he could run things with another job title.
{DIALOGUE}: Wouldn't be the best, but, uh, what are we gonna do?
