{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: STONE walks back to his car.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Both cars pull out in opposite directions.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. TANGIERS SPORTSBOOK/ACES HIGH! THE SAM ROTHSTEIN SHOW - NIGHT
