{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She walks across the room to ACE's desk.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: GINGER
{DIALOGUE}: So don't let him come in here 'cause I know they're in here in the desk and he's -
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She tries to open the middle drawer but it's locked.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: GINGER
{DIALOGUE}: Fuck!
{META_DATA}: (Going through a couple of drawers.)
{DIALOGUE}: Just pay attention.
{DIALOGUE}: He could come up here at any time.
{META_DATA}: (Pants.)
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She spots a pair of scissors on the desk.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She tries to open the drawer with them.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: GINGER
{META_DATA}: (Then, to COP #2)
{DIALOGUE}: Are you watching for him?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She finally pries the drawer open, breaking the tip of the scissors.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: GINGER's hands open the drawer and she picks up the safe deposit keys.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: GINGER
{DIALOGUE}: Got 'em.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: FREEZE FRAME ON THE GLIMMERING KEYS.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. ACE'S HOUSE - MORNING
