{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: GAGGI
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: has a cane in front of him.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Several court spectators look on.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: We hear the bosses' lawyer speak.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LAWYER
